話買入價只係心理上的問題，唔重要咁，不斷洗你腦，令你覺得只有一個方法買股致富，就buy and hold。 令你覺得自己守住d 股票有壓力下只係唔夠正面，唔夠信心，唔夠堅持。最後都係失敗，就自己D7 自己，咁個意志就消沉，再loop。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手法3 (Hustle culture (in x成 case: Blind hold culture)): 不斷重覆投資成功在於Strong hold (Blind strong hold)，there is no other ways. 跟著你strong hold 唔得，因為你唔夠長，唔夠「50年」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n後記: 我睇過x 成d 書，就係有d concept 啱，有d concept 錯先抵死，所以有大量人信佢，then 可能入左上述的looping。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: d 人問我買股，我只會話QQQ, ARKK ，簡單好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cf6f8cb835a46d029b25d9fccfff4ddda5c0c9","tid":2360171,"uid":258948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T08:22:46.000Z","msg":"龔成老師再獻新猷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016f45b586d48e6eafce19be4a12cc9302350985","tid":2360171,"uid":258948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8691ca5225cd9a12e265745a8abec32d4e52ecc5","tid":2360171,"uid":127905,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T14:55:14.000Z","msg":"識睇一定睇留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JhE8eN2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJhE8eN2.png&h=3342b187&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"很有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真如果得個四萬本，不如用黎學野增值自己/洗左佢叫雞溝女乜都好好過"},{"pid":"dbd2f1f4ab714cfa1f397fad92e26a609abaab03","tid":2360171,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTim